pos_examples: Now, take image of objective teddy in mode rain using camera frame_9 on rover dress_red at waypoint fire.

First, drop contents from store kumquat_8 of rover object_50 and then communicate image data from rover socket at waypoint screen to lander object_260 at waypoint screen_64 for objective bastion in mode star_213.

(drop object_50 kumquat_8)
(communicate_image_data socket object_260 bastion star_213 screen screen_64)
